Rizal: And yet they do not fully show the achievements of our people before colonization.
filipinoscholars: You plan to annotate these texts?
Rizal: Yes. Our history must be told from our own perspective.
"european scholar": That may challenge established narratives.
Rizal: Then it is necessary. Truth must not remain hidden.
filipinoscholars: Your work may change how Filipinos see themselves.
Rizal: That is my hope. A nation must understand its past to shape its future.